            <fr:title text="Locally distributed space">Locally distributed space</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  A <html:em>locally distributed space</html:em> is a pair <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[(X,\mathcal {O}_{X})]]></fr:tex>, where <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is a topological space and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {O}_{X}]]></fr:tex> is a sheaf of local distributive lattice on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
